; Coverage for value.cc
; When --exchange specifies a source:target pair and the source commodity
; does not exist in the commodity pool, sources.push_back(nullptr) is
; called. Here NONEXIST is not a known commodity.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    100 EUR
    Assets:Cash      -$120.00

P 2024/01/01 EUR $1.20

test bal --exchange NONEXIST:$
            $-120.00  Assets:Cash
             $120.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
